**R1 — Dimitroff contact data:** Resolved. Phone (806) 316-5296, 120 Amherst Ave Dumas TX 79029, hours Mon-Fri 8am-6pm / Sat-Sun 10am-5pm, BBB accredited — all present.

**R2 — Competitor landscape:** Resolved. Identified 4 named competitors (Overhead Door Co. Amarillo, Price Overhead, Willow Creek, Integrity), all with zero city LPs outside Amarillo. Gap strategy documented per city.

**R3 — SEO analyzer:** Resolved. GH Pages app confirmed at `mwegter95.github.io/free-seo-analyzer-with-js-rendering/`. Backend routes `/auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/seo/analyze` confirmed existing. No rebuild — link/embed only. Demo flow documented.

**R4 — City list:** Resolved. 12 city LPs (9 TX + 3 NM) with differentiated content angles per city.

**Architecture:** Complete. WP theme file map (12 PHP templates), Docker compose with creds, port 8090 confirmed, Maryland bridge clone path specified with all required filters called out verbatim. Plugin stack, schema types per page, conversion architecture, technical SEO checklist — all specified. Traceability matrix covers every posting requirement. Design system bespoke (not portfolio look).

**CLAUDE.md compliance:** ASCII-only runner scripts, no `?>` PHP closing tags, Docker service registration (not blocking runner), cloudflare tunnel untouched — all acknowledged in plan.

**No gaps remain.** Plan is complete and actionable.

